 <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=63903&amp;start=13\">Re: Symmetric multiprocessing (SMP) scaling - SF8 and K10.4</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 06, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65791\">Wasp 2.60 by John Stanback released!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 22, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65805\">Wasp and a question</a> by <a href=\"/Fernando_Villegas\" title=\"Fernando Villegas\">Fernando Villegas</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 23, 2017</li></ul>\n<p><b>2018</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67410\">Wasp 3.00 available ...</a>  by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68154&amp;start=7\">Re: Lazy SMP and 44 cores</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69256\">Wasp 3.50 by John Stanback available!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2018</li></ul>\n<p><b>2019</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70444\">Wasp 3.60 available (for DGT Pi too, for chess computer lovers)</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 07, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/DGT_Pi\" title=\"DGT Pi\">DGT Pi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71744\">Wasp 3.75 by John Stanback released ...</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 06, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=74174\">Wasp 4.00 by John Stanback available!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75794\">Wasp NN</a> by <a href=\"/Ted_Summers\" title=\"Ted Summers\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 14, 2020</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75794&amp;start=4\">Re: Wasp NN</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 14, 2020</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75896\">Wasp 4.08 dev</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 22, 2020</li></ul>\n<p><b>2021</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76205\">Wasp 4.5 Released</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 01, 2021</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76205&amp;start=14\">Re: Wasp 4.5 Released</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 03, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=78687\">Wasp 5.00 released</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2021</li></ul>\n<p><b>2022</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=79034\">Wasp 5.20 Released</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2022</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=79675\">Wasp 5.50 Released</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 12, 2022</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.amateurschach.de/main/_wasp.htm\">Frank's Chess Page, Wasp by John Stanback</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://computerchess.org.uk/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Wasp&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Wasp</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/15</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/WASP\">WASP - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/wasp\">wasp - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wasp\">Wasp from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wasp_(disambiguation)\">Wasp (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/W.A.S.P.\">W.A.S.P.</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.azlyrics.com/lyrics/wasp/mantronic.html\">Mantronic</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inside_the_Electric_Circus\">Inside the Electric Circus</a> (1986), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/JrF2btiNBCg?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wasp&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vespula\">Vespula</a> is a small genus of social wasps, widely distributed in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Hemisphere\">Northern Hemisphere</a>. Along with members of their sister genus <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dolichovespula\">Dolichovespula</a>, they are collectively known by the common name <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yellow_jacket\">yellow jackets</a> (or yellow-jackets) in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_America\">North America</a>. Vespula species have a shorter malar space and a more pronounced tendency to nest underground, but are otherwise nearly indistinguishable from Dolichovespula. As shown a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vespula_germanica\">Vespula germanica</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Vespula_germanica_Richard_Bartz.jpg\">Image</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Richard_Bartz\">Richard Bartz</a>, August 10, 2007, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.5/deed.en\">CC BY-SA 2.5</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wasp\">Wasp from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60550\">Wasp 1.01 x64 by John Stanback released ...</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 22, 2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.amateurschach.de/main/_wasp.htm\">Frank's Chess Page, Wasp by John Stanback</a>, June 22, 2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63783\">Wasp 2.00 by John Stanback ... with Lazy SMP!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2017</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75794&amp;start=4\">Re: Wasp NN</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 14, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=78687\">Wasp 5.00 released</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2021</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">based on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.amateurschach.de/main/wasp/release_notes_101.txt\">Wasp Release Notes</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228095958\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.085 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.620 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 154/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 326/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:3230-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228095957 and revision id 26445\n -->\n"
